          "block_label": "formula",
          "block_content": "\\mathbf{A}=\\left[\\begin{matrix}{a_{_{11}}}&{a_{_{12}}}&{\\cdots}&{a_{_{1n}}}\\\\ {a_{_{21}}}&{a_{_{22}}}&{\\cdots}&{a_{_{2n}}}\\\\ {\\cdot}&{\\cdot}&{\\cdots}&{\\cdot}\\\\ {a_{_{m1}}}&{a_{_{m2}}}&{\\cdots}&{a_{_{m n}}}\\\\ \\end{matrix}\\right],\\quad\\mathrm{~a n d~}\\quad\\mathbf{x}=\\left[\\begin{matrix}{x_{_{1}}}\\\\ {\\cdot}\\\\ {\\cdot}\\\\ {\\cdot}\\\\ {x_{_{n}}}\\\\ \\end{matrix}\\right]\\quad\\mathrm{~a n d~}\\quad\\mathbf{b}=\\left[\\begin{matrix}{b_{_{1}}}\\\\ {\\vdots}\\\\ {b_{_{m}}}\\\\ \\end{matrix}\\right]",
